title: Its Over # 978 (Ep 978)
description:

Lindsey Graham explodes on the Democrats in this cable news appearance.

Here’s video of Joe Biden calling for a forty foot high border fence. 

This “raw intelligence” nonsense line has got to stop.

Harvard cowers and bows down to the social justice warriors.
